<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei di'n kipak a um,
 Hukdampa hung pieng chu;
 Mahleh van mite ka thilin,
 A ngaih pen uh - Hukdampa,
 Thaknan zaila a sau.

[V2]
 2. Na Cha khat neihsun chu,
 Nunnawpna cheng nusie'n;
 Gimtheih thawk guol loh chu Na thawk sak
 Nei hehpih zie lawm lawm hi,
 Gentheih ding guol ei puoi,

[V3]
 3. Ka Tanpa hung pieng chu,
 Khawitak ah ka hawl dem?
 Bethlehem dai bawng In sungah
 Aw ka thagau va chieh in,
 Na Tanpa kawm a chun.

[V4]
 4. Hawl zel in ka thagau,
 Na Lalpa hung pieng chu;
 Amah chu ei Puipa ahi,
 Angel ven vangkhawlun ah,
 Bittaka ei tun ding.

[V5]
 5. Van ah ei tun ina.
 Van Lal cha genthei chun;
 A kipahna chanpih dingin,
 Lunga ka gelin Lalpa,
 Kipak lothei kei puoi.

[V6]
 6. Aw Lalpa kei u di'n
 Na cha deih mah mah chu,
 Bethlehem bawng In ah Na piensak,
 Aw hehpihna bukim chu.
 Nang in na nei zo ie.</lyrics>
<title>Ei Tanpa Chu !</title>
<hymn_number>33</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
</song>